==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Close-stool
<hw>Close"-stool`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A utensil to
hold a chamber vessel, for the use of the sick and infirm. It is usually
in the form of a box, with a seat and tight cover.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Closet</ent>⟦br⟧
